    <!--Project Intro-->
      <p>Food bloggers and influencers often go restaurant-hopping, hitting as many spots in the same area. While this saves travel time, the proximity of the stops make the trip less than ideal. For this self-tracking project, I wanted to visualize the progression of my calorie gain and/or loss during a pizza hop around Lower Manhattan to see if the trip was worth it.</p>
