    <div class="col-md-2-5ths">
      <!--Project Content-->
      <strong>Data Collection</strong><br><br>
      I had my sights set on Lower Manhattan due to the number of popular (and some of my favorite) pizza parlors in the area. To further narrow down my options, I drew a route shaped like a pizza slice that hit six spots!<br>
        <img src="<%= image_path("images/project-pizza/map.PNG") %>" class="zoomImages" style="width:50%;" alt="My pizza hopping route">
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-5ths">
      <!--Project Intro-->
      <br><br>In preparation for my pizza hop, I defined the data values to track throughout the trip–<br><br>
      <strong>Dimensions:</strong> Pizzeria, pizza flavor<br>
      <strong>Measures:</strong> Calories gained, calories lost, time of arrival, time of departure, time spent, distance travelled<br><br>
        I used both Google Maps and the Health app on my phone to record my data.
    </div>
