      <strong>Preparing the Pizza</strong><br><br>
      Now for the fun part! I prepared the pizza crust and my choice of toppings: truffle oil, red pepper, mushrooms, baby spinach, and some kale-spinach pesto. I used fresh spinach to represent calories gained and then pesto (ground up spinach, among other ingredients) for calories lost, emphasizing the gain vs. loss relationship.<br><br>
      <img src="<%= image_path("images/project-pizza/ingredients.JPG") %>" class="zoomImages" alt=""><br><br>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-5ths">
      <br><br>The slope of the bell pepper strips shows the 'stretch' of time spent in every stop on the trip.
    </div>
  </div>

